cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on transfer learning for image classification using CNNs, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of semantic and content-based similarities, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a methodology for improving the transfer learning process, which involves the use of supplementary weights, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
